OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers this evening. Then the rest of
OL,7,Fthe night will be dry with clear
OL,8,Fperiods and just the odd shower. Cold
OL,9,Fwith patchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FMost of the day will be dry,
OL,12,Fsome early brightness. Outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain spreading east from late
OL,14,Fafternoon into the evening.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRain at
OL,17,Ffirst on Friday then drier with a few
OL,18,Fshowers. Cloudy on Saturday with rain,
OL,19,Foccasionally heavy, spreading east.
OL,20,FCold and bright on Sunday with
OL,21,Fblustery showers, severe gales
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
